object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM metal.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT  
		metal_atg.source_name, 
		metal_atg.load_type, 
		metal_atg.agency_nup, 
		metal_atg.created, 
		metal_atg.effective_date, 
		metal_atg.gw_producer_id, 
		metal_atg.id, 
		metal_atg.lob, 
		metal_atg.modified,
		metal_atg.new_date,
		metal_atg.noticeto_agent,
		metal_atg.renewal_date,
		metal_atg.replaced_by,
		metal_atg.state,
		metal_atg.sub_code,
		metal_atg.type,
		current_batch.batch_id
FROM metal.adm_termination_guidewire metal_atg
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
    metal_atg.id,
    metal_atg.created,
    metal_atg.modified;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: o_src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5(
	'source_name' || source_name || 
	'load_type' || load_type || 
	'o_termination_guidewire_datetime_created' || to_char(o_termination_guidewire_datetime_created) || 
	'o_termination_guidewire_datetime_modified' || to_char(o_termination_guidewire_datetime_modified) || 
	'o_agency_id' || to_char(o_agency_id) ||
    'o_termination_guidewire_effective_date'|| to_char(o_termination_guidewire_effective_date)||
    'gw_producer_id' || gw_producer_id || 
	'o_termination_guidewire_id' || to_char(o_termination_guidewire_id) 
	|| 'lob' || lob ||
    'o_new_business_termination_date' || to_char(o_new_business_termination_date)
	|| 'noticeto_agent' || noticeto_agent || 
	'o_renewal_termination_date' || to_char(o_renewal_termination_date)
	|| 'replaced_by' || replaced_by 
	|| 'state' || state || 
	'sub_code' || sub_code || 
	'type' || type 
	)

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
        termination_guidewire_row_id, 
        termination_guidewire_row_md5checksum, 
        termination_guidewire_id,  
  termination_guidewire_datetime_created,
  termination_guidewire_datetime_modified	
    FROM bronze.adm_termination_guidewire
    where  termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
